---
title: Beyond Meat® and Feta Meatballs with Dilly Orzo and Spinach
description: We've transformed the delicious flavours of spanakopita into a weeknight orzo bowl! Each Beyond Meat® meatball will delight your tastebuds with a bite of melty, briny feta!
